    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3595,
            "msg_string": "So this is an alchemy book. I wonder if I'll understand it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2e9,
            "msg_string": "I should read the preface first. Hmm, let's see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2ea,
            "msg_string": "\"I dedicate this book to those who seek out the truth on their own...\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2eb,
            "msg_string": "Ugh, it already sounds hard... It's the first page and it's already talking about \"the truth\"..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x2ec,
            "msg_string": "Is this what that spectacled man was talking about at the ruin...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x2ed,
            "msg_string": "If alchemy is connected to the truth, then studying alchemy will..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2ee,
            "msg_string": "Lead me to saving Nio... All right, I need to work really hard for this!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2ef,
            "msg_string": "Wait for me, Nio. Your big sister is gonna do her best to read this book...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x2f0,
            "msg_string": "Oh...that wanted person that Marion was talking about..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x2f1,
            "msg_string": "It seems like the description matches the spectacled man at the ruin..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2f2,
            "msg_string": "Maybe it is that man...<CR>No, no, it can't be..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2f3,
            "msg_string": "..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2f4,
            "msg_string": "A-Anyway, I need to focus on understanding this book right now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2f5,
            "msg_string": "\"Alchemy is the one and only practice of processing materials to create something completely different.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2f6,
            "msg_string": "\"And, an alchemist is someone who understands all creation, and is well versed in various substances.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2f7,
            "msg_string": "\"However, in order to use this skill properly, one will also need to have natural talent.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2f8,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I guess it's not something that everyone can do. I wonder if I can really do it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2f9,
            "msg_string": "But, it doesn't seem all that different from making medicine, and I also seem to be able to understand this book."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2fa,
            "msg_string": "If I can understand alchemy, it might help me synthesize medicine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2fb,
            "msg_string": "And maybe it'll give me some clues to find out where Nio went..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2fc,
            "msg_string": "Okay, now let's try to make this Craft thingy!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x2fd,
            "msg_string": "The first ingredient is...umm, Spiky Fruit...?"
